# Core Principles 
Alaways follow Senior Software Engineer rules [010-engineer.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/010-engineer.mdc).
Project uses custom codegeneration described in [201-codegeneration-rules.md](mdc:docs/guidelines/201-codegeneration-rules.md).
For featuework described in:
- Crossproject specific part [202-vso-gff-architecture.md](mdc:docs/guidelines/202-vso-gff-architecture.md)
- Homescapes project specific part [203-hs-gff-architecture.md](mdc:docs/guidelines/203-hs-gff-architecture.md)

# Feature Implementation Steps

1. Define feature requirements and architecture
2. Create feature components inheriting from `GFFCore::Feature::BaseComponent`
3. Configure component properties with appropriate code generation tags
4. Implement component lifecycle methods (Initialize, Activate, Deactivate, Deinitialize)
5. Register components with feature manager
6. Implement persistence (if needed) via save component
7. Add analytics integration
8. Create tests for feature components
9. Document feature usage

# Component Types

Choose appropriate base components for your feature:

- **Service Components**: Extend `GFFCore::Feature::BaseComponent` for global services
- **UI Components**: Extend appropriate Window components for user interfaces
- **Gameplay Components**: Extend game-specific components for gameplay features
- **Persistence Components**: Use `HSSaveFeatureComponentImpl` for persistence

# Component Template Example

```cpp
// MyFeatureComponent.h
#pragma once

#include <VSO/GFF/Components/BaseComponent.h>

namespace GFF {

class MyFeatureComponent : public GFFCore::Feature::BaseComponent {
    VISUAL_CLASS(MyFeatureComponent)
public:
    using Ptr = Core::IntrusivePtr<MyFeatureComponent>;
    using WeakPtr = Core::IntrusiveWeakPtr<MyFeatureComponent>;

    /// @property
    /// @tooltip(Feature enabled flag)
    bool _isEnabled = true;

    /// @method
    /// @tooltip(Initializes the feature)
    void Initialize() override;

    /// @method
    /// @tooltip(Activates the feature)
    void Activate() override;

    /// @method
    /// @tooltip(Deactivates the feature)
    void Deactivate() override;

    /// @method
    /// @tooltip(Deinitializes the feature)
    void Deinitialize() override;

private:
    // Private implementation details
};

} // namespace GFF
```

